{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Brigand: Panama</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Four years after the events of Oaxaca, the Pirate Kingdoms are ravaged by civil war, and another wave of refugees is crashing into the mainland to escape the bloodshed. Ozee and his crew are bound for Panama, where there is rumor of an old Baroque facility deep in the jungle that contains technology that will help turn the tides and establish dominance over the islands once again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The player must stop them, or help them. Either way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>New Features:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Completely new story and setting that will take about 12 hours to complete, with high replayability. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-New items, including clams, bamboo, spears, smoking pipes, fishing rods, flamethrowers, cryo grenades, homing rockets, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-New baddies, including animated skeletons, shamans, cyber hounds, fire loa, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-New cast of characters with unique personalities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Woodcraft ability for crafting bamboo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-A shit-ton of traps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-New Game+ option when you win, allowing you to restart the story with your end-game character and inventory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/709830/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737216187","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/709830/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737216187","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/709830/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737216187","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/ap